          "text": "如此甚妙，只有一件，高杰镇守扬通，兵骄将傲，那黄刘三镇，每发不平之恨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "侯方域",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日相见，大费调停，万一兄弟不和，岂不为敌人之利乎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史可法",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "所说极是。今日相见，俺自有一番劝慰之言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "辕门传鼓，说四镇到齐，伺候参谒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（侯方域下，史可法升帐。吹打〖大开门〗。仪卫排左右，高杰、黄德功、刘泽清、刘良佐穿甲胄同上。吹"
        },
        {
          "character": "书童",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打住。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "高杰、黄德功、刘泽清、刘良佐",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只恨燕京无乐毅，谁知江左有夷吾。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（高杰、黄德功、刘泽清、刘良佐同见。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "高杰、黄德功、刘泽清、刘良佐",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四镇小将叩谒阁部大元帅。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（高杰、黄德功、刘泽清、刘良佐同拜，史可法拱手立。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "史可法",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列位请起。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（高杰、黄德功、刘泽清、刘良佐同排立。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "高杰、黄德功、刘泽清、刘良佐",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听候元帅将令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史可法",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本帅，以阁部皆师，君命隆重，大小将士俱在指挥之下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高杰、黄德功、刘泽清、刘良佐",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史可法",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四镇乃堂堂列侯，不比寻常武弁。屈尊伺坐，共议军情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高杰、黄德功、刘泽清、刘良佐",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史可法",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本帅命坐，便如军令一般，不可推辞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高杰、黄德功、刘泽清、刘良佐",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。告坐了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（高杰首座，黄德功、刘泽清、刘良佐依次坐，黄德功怒视高杰。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "史可法 （混江龙） 淮南险要，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "江河保障势滔滔。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "满目细柳垂条。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "犀军放弩早惊潮。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "比得上绛、灌、萧、曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "同心共把乾坤造。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "似今日列侯公剑佩弓刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄德功怒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄德功",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅在上，小将本不该争论。这高杰乃投诚草寇，有何战功？今日公然坐俺三"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄德功",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "镇之上，俨然以副帅自居，是何道理？"
        },
        {
          "character": "高杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我投诚最早，年齿又尊，岂肯居尔等之下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘泽清",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我想此处是你的汛地，我们到此都是客宾，你连宾主之礼都不晓得，还要统兵？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘良佐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他在扬州享受繁华，尊大惯了，今日也该让咱们享享。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们哪个敢来，我就奉让。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄德功",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两位刘兄同我出来，即刻与那厮见个高低。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄德功、刘泽清、刘良佐同怒下，史可法向高杰。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "史可法",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他们讲的有道理，你还该谦让他们才是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小将宁死不肯相让！"
        },
        {
          "character": "史可法",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这就大错了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（油葫芦） 四镇堂堂气象豪，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倚仗着恢复北朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恰似好同胞。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "失了同心好，斗齿牙，变了协恭貌。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一个儿，眼睁睁同室操戈盾；"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一个儿，怒冲冲平地起波涛。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "早已窝里相争闹。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "封了一伙小儿曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史可法",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不料四镇英雄，可笑如此。老夫一天高兴，却早灰冷一半也。没奈何，且出张"
        },
        {
          "character": "史可法",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告示，晓谕三镇，叫他各回汛地听候调遣。你既驻扎本境，就在本帅标下做个"
        },
        {
          "character": "史可法",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先锋，各有执掌，他们也不敢来争闹了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢元帅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史可法",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待老夫写起告示来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（史可法写，内呐喊。黄德功、刘泽清、刘良佐持刀同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄德功、刘泽清、刘良佐",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "高杰快快出来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "高杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "青天白日持刀呐喊，竟是反了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄德功",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们为什么反？只要杀你这个无礼贼子！"
        },
        {
          "character": "高杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们敢在帅府门前如此放肆，难道不是无礼贼子吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄德功、刘泽清、刘良佐同追杀高杰，高杰入辕门叫。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "高杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阁部大老爷，救命呀！黄、刘三贼杀入帅府来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄德功、刘泽清、刘良佐同外骂，史可法惊立。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "史可法",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（天下乐） 俺只道，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "塞马南来把战挑。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "却是咱兵自鏖。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎当的阋墙鼓噪，起了离间根苗。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这才是将难调，北贼易讨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史可法",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快请侯相公出来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙套",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侯爷有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（侯方域急上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "侯方域",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晚生已听得明白了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史可法",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "借重高才，传俺帅令，安抚乱军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "侯方域",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如何安抚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "史可法",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫有告示一纸，快去晓谕他们便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "侯方域",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（侯方域接告示，见。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "侯方域",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列侯请了！小弟乃本府参谋，奉阁部大元帅之命，晓谕三镇知悉：恭逢新主中"
        },
        {
          "character": "侯方域",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兴，闯贼未讨，正我辈枕戈待旦，立功报效之时，不宜怀挟小忿，致乱大谋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "侯方域",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俟收复中原，太平赐宴，论功叙坐，自有朝仪。目下军容匆遽，凡事权宜，皆"
        },
        {
          "character": "侯方域",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当相谅，无失旧好。兴平侯高，原镇扬、通，今即留在本帅标下，委作先锋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "侯方域",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "靖安侯黄，仍回庐和。东平侯刘，仍回淮徐。广昌侯刘，仍回凤、泗。静听调"
        },
        {
          "character": "侯方域",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遣，勿得违抗。军法凛然，本帅不能容情也。特谕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄德功",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们只要杀死无礼贼子，怎敢犯元帅军法。"
        },
        {
          "character": "侯方域",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "目今辕门截杀，这就是军法难容的了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘泽清",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既是这等，不要惊着元帅，大家且散。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘良佐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "明日杀到高杰家里去罢。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "刘良佐",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "国仇犹可恕，私恨最难消。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄德功、刘泽清、刘良佐同下，侯方域入见史可法。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "侯方域",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三镇闻令，暂且退散去，明日还要厮杀哩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史可法",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这便怎么处？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（后庭花） 高将军，你横将仇衅招，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为甚的不谦恭，妄自骄；"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "惹动他诸侯五路刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也不过息兵半晌饶。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "费调停，干焦躁。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "难消释，空懊恼。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那事业全去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "元帅不必着急，明日和他见个输赢，把三镇人马并俺一处，随着元帅恢复中原，"
        },
        {
          "character": "高杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "却亦不难也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史可法",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你说的是哪里话，现今流寇北来，将渡黄河。总兵许定国，不能阻挡，连夜告"
        },
        {
          "character": "史可法",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "急；正要与四镇商议，发兵防河。今日一动争端，误俺大事，岂不可忧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "高杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他三镇也不为别的，只因扬州繁华，要来夺取，俺怎肯让他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史可法",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这话益发可笑了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（煞尾） 引领着一支兵，和他三家傲，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "似垒卵泰山压倒。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不教你蕃鳌观独琼花少。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史可法",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妒杀你腰缠十万好。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（煞尾） 怕明日，杀声咽断广陵涛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史可法",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢，罢，罢！老夫已拚一死，更无他法。侯兄大才，只索凭你筹划了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "侯方域",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且看局势，再做商量。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗，〖大开门〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "侯方域",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掩门。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下，史可法，侯方域同下，高杰吊场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "高杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺高杰也是一条好汉，难道坐以待毙不成。明早黄金坝上，点齐人马，排下阵"
        },
        {
          "character": "高杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "势，等他来时，迎敌便了。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "高杰",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "龙争虎斗逞雄豪，杯酒筵边动剑刀。刘项何须成败论，将军头断不降曹。"
        }
      ],
